							<p>7.2 Third Party Posts. Despite these restrictions, please be aware that some material provided by users may be objectionable, unlawful, inaccurate, or inappropriate. Discovered does not endorse any User Material, and User Material that is Posted does not reflect the opinions or policies of Discovered. We reserve the right, but have no obligation, to monitor User Material and to restrict or remove User Material that we determine, in our sole discretion, is inappropriate or for any other business reason, as permitted by law. In no event does Discovered assume any responsibility or liability whatsoever for any User Material, and you agree to waive any legal or equitable rights or remedies you may have against Discovered with respect to such User Material. You can help us tremendously by notifying us of any inappropriate User Material you find by emailing <a href="mailto:help@Discovered.tv?subject=Inappropriate User Material" class="policies_link" target="_blank">help@Discovered.tv</a> (subject line: "Inappropriate User Material").</p>
							
